  "texts": [
    "On the other hand, government, and non-governmental organizations (NGOs) could also provide subsidies and microloans tailored to technology adoption.",
    "Similarly, establishing community centers where farmers could access AI tools and resources could save them from immense individual costs.",
    "In a similar manner, AI technology could be offered on rental or subscription basis to reduce the upfront costs.",
    "• Infrastructure presents a huge challenge in the adoption of AI.",
    "Limited access to electricity hinders the execution of AI-driven devices."
  ]
}